wpt.desc: Rambo's Cache by Candystick, Traditional Cache (2.5/1)

groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:name: Rambo's Cache
groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:short_description: This is a micro cache. Cache is only big enough for a log so bring your own pen.
groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:long_description:
Micro cache hidden on a small bridge that we spotted while on a visit to the US. The bridges' Engineer was N.R.Rambo, hence the name. Take your time looking around for the cache and watch for muggles. Parking available right near the bridge.
As we are not natives to this continent, the "Pirates of Penn" will be maintaining the cache for us. Please contact them if there are any issues.

groundspeak:log.groundspeak:text: This is what I like about caching -- I've lived within a few miles of this stream for years but never noticed it before.
